com.JasonILTG.ScienceMod.item.general

Interface IItemScienceMod

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IScienceModContent
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractArmorUpgrade, ArmorScience, ArmorScienceSpecial, Battery, CompoundItem, Exoskeleton, ExoUpgrade, Hull, ItemElement, ItemJarred, ItemScience, ItemWireCoil, JarItem, JarLauncher, Mixture, PowerBlock, PowerCapacityUpgrade, PowerInputUpgrade, PowerOutputUpgrade, ScienceComponent, ScienceUpgrade, Solution, SpeedUpgrade, TemperatureGauge

    public interface IItemScienceMod
extends IScienceModContent
    Interface for all items in this mod.

    Any class implementing this interface must extend net.minecraft.item.Item in some way.

    Author:
    JasonILTG and syy1125
